metadata.name: Control
metadata.description:
Control over destiny 
This picture will tell you about control. Remember, have you ever had a situation when you felt that you were under control and you could not escape? It's like there are chains on your hands, invisible and thin, but for you they are heavy and indestructible. And you fall to your knees, unable to resist and fight. And only the power inside, the voice, as if from outer space, lifts you up like a puppet, suddenly you feel that you can break the shackles, that only you can control your destiny. 
And again your body begins to shine like a star in the night, to shine with life and desire for freedom. Stretching out your hands to the cosmos, the chains on your wrists are destroyed and you realize that only you can control your fate. 
No one else has that right. 
Forward to the stars.
